00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:27.600
The Colt is a gun that has a maximun damage of 100% in the head and a minimun damage of 40% in the arms or legs.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:31.720
It has a capacity of 7 bullets in every charger and a range of 100 meters.

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:37.100
It supports tactic accesories and occupy 4 slots in the inventory, 2 of high by 2 wide.

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:44.340
The Cobra is a gun that has a maximun damage of 100% in the head and a minimun damage of 40% in the arms or legs.

00:00:44.340 --> 00:00:49.180
