00:00:49.180 --> 00:00:54.980
It supports tactic and barrel accesories and occupy 4 slots in the inventory, 2 of high by 2 wide.

00:00:54.980 --> 00:01:00.600
The Ace is a gun that has a maximun damage of 100% in the head and a minimun damage of 40% in the arms or legs.

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:04.440
