00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:09.700
It doesn't support any type of accesories and occupy 4 slots in the inventory, 2 of high by 2 wide.

00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:16.740
The Schofield is a rifle that has a maximun damage of 100% in the head and a minimun damage of 25% in the arms or legs.

00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:20.560
